O que se passa?



592
00:47:33,840 --> 00:47:35,398
Vão Ievã-Io pan o Septo de Baelor.



593
00:47:35,560 --> 00:47:37,869
- A quem?
- À Mão do Rei!



594
00:48:42,600 --> 00:48:45,034
- Traidor!
- Cobarde!



595
00:48:45,200 --> 00:48:46,758
Baelor.



596
00:48:46,999 --> 00:48:48,637
Baelor!



597
00:48:54,120 --> 00:48:57,237
Traidor! Traidor!



598
00:49:15,200 --> 00:49:19,432
Sou Eddard Stark,
senhor de Winterfell



599
